data.description: Gorgeous 3 bedroom/ 2.5 bathroom end unit townhouse with a water view in a maintenance free gated community! As you walk inside your eyes are drawn to the soaring 20ft ceilings with an abundance of natural light spilling into the room. Master bedroom is on the first floor, relax in your master bath retreat complete with dual sinks, large shower, garden tub and walk in closet with built ins. The gourmet kitchen has all stainless-steel appliances, granite counter tops, up graded cook top, a large walk- in pantry and an eat-in kitchen. Upstairs, there is a spacious loft/play area that overlooks the first floor with built ins.The highly desirable gated Palma Vista community features include two unheated pools available year round, fitness center, and clubhouse available. Tampa Palms is conveniently located to many wonderful restaurants, shopping centers, golf courses, USF, hospitals, the airport and quick access to I 75 and I 275!
